## Day 4 (2026-07-10)

### Goal

Reduce OpenAI API cost by optimizing workflow execution.

### Problem

Google Sheets returned multiple rows.

Previous workflow:

Google Sheets
↓
Basic LLM Chain
↓
OpenAI

Each row triggered a separate OpenAI request.

Result:

5 rows
↓
5 OpenAI Calls
↓
~6183 Tokens

### Solution

Implemented Aggregate node.

Workflow:

Manual Trigger
↓
Google Sheets
↓
Aggregate
↓
Basic LLM Chain
↓
OpenAI Chat Model

### Result

5 rows
↓
1 Aggregated Dataset
↓
1 OpenAI Call
↓
~517 Tokens

### Improvement

Estimated token reduction:

6183 → 517

Approximately 90% reduction.

### Key Learning

A workflow that works is not necessarily a workflow that scales.

Scalability and cost optimization are critical when building AI products.
